title: Ballard super cute studio apartment home, call today for a private vie
posting_body: ['Call today to schedule your private viewing of this charming, classic apartment home in the heart of Ballard!', 'This apartment boasts large North & West facing windows for ample light.', 'Newer paint, carpet and vinyl.', 'BONUS 8X6 room!', 'Plenty of storage closets and we welcome cats (meow!).', 'The Bayview is a small community of 8 apartments conveniently located close to shopping, restaurants, neighborhood shops and parks.', 'Easy access to the Metro bus line and only 15 minutes from the University of Washington and downtown Seattle.', 'Ready for move in August 4th!', 'KEY FEATURES', 'Rent: $1250/month', 'Bedrooms: Studio w/8X6 bonus room', 'Bathrooms: 1', 'Parking: On street', 'Lease Duration: 1 Year (See Details Below)', 'Deposit: $800/Security, $350/Pet (cats only, two pet max)', 'Laundry:', 'In building', 'We ask for: One year lease.', "1st month's rent (last month's rent is not required with approved credit), security deposit $800, pet deposit $350 (cats only/2 pet max), application fee $54 per applicant, water/sewer/garbage/heat/hot water $100/mo per adult occupant.", 'Ready to move in August 4th!', 'We do not accept portable tenant screening reports.', 'Equal Opportunity Housing.', "Under Seattle's Fair Chance Ordinance, SMC 14.09, landlords are prohibited from requiring disclosure, asking about, rejecting an applicant, or taking any adverse action based on any arrest record, conviction record, or criminal history, except for registry information as described in subsection 14.09.025.A.3, 14.09.025.A.4, and 14.09.025.A.5, and subject to the exclusions and legal requirements in Section 14.09.115.", 'Our application and tenant selection policy can be reviewed at <URL>', 'Contact info:', 'Marie', 'Olsen Properties', 'show contact info']
